<item>
            <title>[LU-3172] call lustre_msg_get_opc() only once inside ost_handle()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3172</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;lustre_msg_get_opc() is called a few times inside ost_handle(); there is no real benefit from this, and we can just make one call when entering ost_handle(). There may be other occurrences in the source where this applies, apart from ost_handle(), but I am just making this change here for now, as this is a frequently-called function. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
